articles.title: COVID testing's value shrinks as vaccines beat back virus - The Associated Press
articles.description: WASHINGTON (AP) — Federal health officials’ new, more relaxed recommendations on masks have all but eclipsed another major change in guidance from the government: Fully vaccinated Americans can largely skip getting tested for the coronavirus.
